# {{INSTANCE_NAME}} System Map

## Structure Overview

- `control/`: tracked project policy and durable operating guidance
- `context/normalized/`: tracked normalized truth
- `context/normalized/devices/`: tracked per-device normalized bundles for inventory-managed nodes
- `inventory/`: tracked device and topology definitions
- `research/`: project-specific vendor, platform, and syntax research notes
- `runbooks/`: tracked approved procedures
- `runtime/`: generated volatile session state
- `runtime/devices/`: generated per-device collection state
- `logs/`: generated structured logs
- `state/`: generated checkpoints, backups, rollback manifests
- `raw-audit/`: generated raw collection output
- `raw-audit/devices/`: generated per-device raw collection output

